{"tid":281441,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對女朋友對得耐係咪一定會無感覺or悶？","createTime":"2017-06-12T17:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T12:04:33.000Z","uid":24836,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4e2881c8c47a8a95e61958702f19bec8d07375","tid":281441,"uid":24836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:01:29.000Z","msg":"拍過3次拍， 頭兩次女朋友個樣正常， 開頭熱戀， 成日搞野，但後來都悶， 無乜感覺咁。<br />\n<br />\n依家個女朋友就女神級別， 又有長腿， 開頭一齊會好開心，都係勁熱戀， 成日都覺得佢好靚會經常望住佢， 亦會成日搞野， 搞得好密<br />\n<br />\n但拍耐左，真係相處耐左， 好似已經冇咩感覺， 唔會覺得佢樣超靚，連搞野都唔會話好有熱衷， 唔會扯到行晒。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪個個男人都係咁， 無論當初追到個女朋友幾靚都好， 都一樣會悶， thats why 咁多明星or d 明人食勁多靚女都唔結婚， 玩到真係悶先結婚"},{"pid":"52d4d6ba81c4a3b6cc7560cb05b61f09de5a47d1","tid":281441,"uid":79223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"人之常情<br />\n唔好話男人 女人都會咁"},{"pid":"83e1fb0193a58d5a53c0028d7c1179feddd30b21","tid":281441,"uid":4210,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"你咪又係為咗屌人"},{"pid":"6f50e1ed8ad8c2844eaf5cc4e451f6452548ea63","tid":281441,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪又係為咗屌人</blockquote><br />\n呢句真"},{"pid":"61237e78d03f74294b280c595a13531d41550828","tid":281441,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你咪又係為咗屌人</blockquote><br />\n呢句真</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7b22b17d467335c64857761a1a4b930a807216","tid":281441,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你咪又係為咗屌人</blockquote><br />\n呢句真</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980f835a957c9a8d1d04c6a7bd1f713ad73e3f4d",